snippet.title: ASDAD: All-Stars Dungeons And Diamonds Release Trailer
snippet.description:
GET IT NOW: http://www.giantenemylabs.com/asdad

All-Stars Dungeons and Diamonds is a competitive game where two players face each other in a diamond-collecting race! The player with the largest number of gems at the end of the round wins!
